description:
Hi YouTube, I'm new to this platform and this is my very first animatic! I love Good Omens so so much that I made an animatic from my heart and soul (and a lot of internal screaming) 

Aside from that, I hope you enjoy my little tribute to this book, tv show and fandom of Good Omens!

To the World! 🥂

Note: In the video no one is Eliza or Alexander!!! I just found the lyrics very fitting for the both of them, it's a wholesome situation don't worry!!! Here hugs for everyone 🤗
